# Evaluation-Driven Development (DeepEval + RAGAS)

> Scoped rules for AI evaluation tests. Auto-attached when editing eval files.
> Every AI-powered project ships with measurable quality metrics.

---

## 🎯 Philosophy

Evaluation is NOT optional. Hiring managers in 2026 specifically scan for evaluation-driven
development. Measurable AI quality metrics signal production maturity beyond typical junior
portfolios.

---

## 📦 Framework

- **DeepEval** — pytest-compatible, open-source AI evaluation framework
- **RAGAS** — RAG-specific evaluation (PolicyPulse only)
- **Install:** `pip install deepeval`
- **Run:** `deepeval test run tests/test_eval.py`

---

