## 🚀 CI Integration

```yaml
# In GitHub Actions CI workflow
- name: Run AI evaluation
  run: deepeval test run tests/test_eval.py
  env:
    GOOGLE_API_KEY: ${{ secrets.GOOGLE_API_KEY }}
```

- CI pipeline includes evaluation gate: fail build if scores drop
- Results logged to `logs/evaluation/` for README metrics table
- README includes evaluation metrics table showing latest scores

